  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Extra_Origins_SMP/BH_NU_HEADER.png\" alt=\"Extra Origins SMP\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Extra_Origins_SMP/BH_NU_ABOUT.png\" alt=\"Overview\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This modpack is based on the origins mod, but it has additional mods. It's basically made for multipayer.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Once in a while a new season starts, when that happens most of the mods change, but the origins mod always stays in.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">You can go out on an adventure with your friends, build a giant storage system or become an engineer with one of the technology mods.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Some of the main origins are: Enderian, Elytrian, Merling, Phantom, Blazeborn, Avian, Arachnid, Shulk, Feline and Libra.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Have fun!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a title=\"Discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/uy9QFaQWR7\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Extra_Origins_SMP/BH_NU_DISCORD.png\" alt=\"discord\" /></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Discord server:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br /><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/uy9QFaQWR7\">htt